    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>The University and College Union (UCU) has called for a period of discontinuous strike action across the higher education in response to a national dispute on pay, equality, workload and casualisation.  Strike action took place in December 2021 and now further days are planned for February and March. This is alongside action short of a strike (ASOS) which started on 1 December 2021.   </p>
<p>Following a recent ballot for industrial action UNISON have now notified the University that it is calling on its members to take industrial action, this will consist of one day of strike action during February as part of the same dispute.</p>]]></Value>
